FBIS4-39526 "drsov111_g_94006" FBIS-SOV-94-111 Daily Report 8 Jun 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus Council of Ministers Forms Military Inspection System Council of Ministers Forms Military Inspection System LD0806160894 Minsk Belarusian Foreign Ministry Department of Information in Russian 1702 GMT 8 Jun 94 LD0806160894 Minsk Belarusian Foreign Ministry Department of Information Russian BFN [Text] By decree of the Council of Ministers of the Republic of Belarus, a military inspection has been set up under the Ministry of Defense. This subunit is given the power to monitor the training of troops, the state of hardware, and military-technical property.
